DURATION:PT30M
SUMMARY:RSE coffee break
UID:0c39ef54-783f-42e0-b60b-e7c030c06486@0c39.org
DESCRIPTION:Weekly virtual coffee break: The RSE Finland group invites all 
 interested in research software engineering to the weekly online coffee 
 break at 10:00 (Europe/Helsinki) every Thursday. The coffee break is an 
 informal meeting\, open for everyone to discuss with and listen to others 
 interested in research software engineering. We currently have no pre-
 decided topics\, but never run out of things to say.\nZoom Link: 
 https://aalto.zoom.us/j/62426845282 (Zoom ID 624 2684 5282)\nWebsite: 
 https://nordic-rse.org/communities/finland/#weekly-virtual-coffee-
 break\nHackMD: https://hackmd.io/@nordic-rse/coffeebreak
LOCATION:https://aalto.zoom.us/j/62426845282 (Zoom ID 624 2684 5282)
DTSTAMP:20230112T133100Z
RRULE:FREQ=WEEKLY;UNTIL=20230630T235959
END:VEVENT
